data.description: Beautiful move-in ready home in desirable Unit 20! 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 1,310 square feet. Spacious open floor plan featuring a large family room with vaulted ceiling and gorgeous eat-in kitchen with walk-in pantry. Generously sized primary bedroom with en suite bathroom boasting dual sink vanity, walk-in shower, and luxurious soaking tub. Big fenced back yard has a pergola covered patio and shed. Plenty of space for parking your RV and toys. Come see this lovely home today!
